<p><strong>PoI-3172:</strong> Well. What do you know of the origins of the Scarlet King?</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Montauk:</strong> There are many theories. <a href="/beneath-two-trees">A creature from the abyss</a>, some <a href="/dust-and-blood">shambling thing of old</a>, a <a href="/channeling-flows">denizen of Alagadda</a>&#8230;</p>
