<p><strong>PoI-3172:</strong> Oh, alright, alright. I am sorry. I am not trying to hurt you, doctor, truly. I just want to understand. It's just- it shouldn't have worked. The child should have been born.</p>
<p><em>There is a pause of several seconds.</em></p>
