<p><strong>PoI-3172:</strong> Because I just want to understand. And now I think I do.</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Montauk:</strong> How?</p>
<p><strong>PoI-3172:</strong> You&#8230; I don't know where to begin. Let me go back. I don't think your department has had very much activity in recent months, not after the Hand's attempt to open the gates, right?. Your procedure keeps the girl from giving birth, the <a href="/scp-3838">nomads</a> keep fighting their endless war, the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/kte-2013-kapala-mendes">spears</a> are safely locked away by the Bookburners, and the Devourer- well, there's nothing you can really do about the Devourer now, is there?</p>
<p><strong>Dr. Montauk:</strong> <a href="/scp-2317">SCP-2317</a> isn't SCP-001.</p>
<p><strong>PoI-3172:</strong> <em>Wasn't</em> SCP-001. But the thing is, you've been telling everyone he is. Technically, <em>you're</em> meant to think that he is, if I understand Foundation hierarchies correctly. You are only a level 4, after all.</p>
